h3. Summary

* When moving pages from one space to another, sometimes the following warning message is triggered:

{panel}
The following error(s) occurred:
* Move failed. Ther was a problem contacting the server.
{panel}

h3. Steps to Reproduce
# Go to the page;
# Click on *...* >> *Move*;
# Type the new space and the new parent page;
# Click *Move*.

h3. Expected Results
* Pages are moved properly without any warning/error message.

h3. Actual Results
* Pages are moved, but the following message is shown, leading to believe that the pages were not moved properly:

{panel}
The following error(s) occurred:
* Move failed. Ther was a problem contacting the server.
{panel}

h3.Workaround
* The pages are moved accordingly, so no workaround is needed.
